Detailed Description

cvmx_usbc::_doepmsk

Device OUT Endpoint Common Interrupt Mask Register (DOEPMSK)

This register works with each of the Device OUT Endpoint Interrupt (DOEPINTn) registers for all endpoints to generate an interrupt per OUT endpoint. The OUT endpoint interrupt for a specific status in the DOEPINTn register can be masked by writing into the corresponding bit in this register. Status bits are masked by default. Mask interrupt: 1'b0 Unmask interrupt: 1'b1
